            <title>[MAHOUT-1033] Solution for MAHOUT-848 doesn&apos;t check for the Configuration object being null before using it.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1033</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A patch was supplied for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-848&quot; title=&quot;M/R job launching code should add Oozie&amp;#39;s action.xml as a configuration resource of the Hadoop Configuration object&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-848&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-848&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; but it didn&apos;t check for the Configuration object being null before using it, so now Mahout jobs will throw an NPE when run in oozie (which is why I marked this ticket as major).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;oozie integration&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
